  ('social-worker-moex-08232', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '將預算制定過程及決策視為過去之預算制定過程及決策的延伸，決策受歷史及過去預算決策的影響之預算制定模式稱為：', '["理性規劃模式", "漸進增值模式", "政治模式", "經濟模式 （請接背面） 律師、會計師、社會工作師 全一張 98年專門職業及技術人員高等考試 考試試題  代號：9 0240 不動產估價師、專利師 （背面） 類    科： 社會工作師"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08233', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那一項有關預算的敘述是正確的？', '["預算等於會計", "預算系統在機構裡是一項獨立的活動", "預算具有控制的功能", "預算是一份不需管理即會自動生效的文件"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08234', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '方案結束後，評估其所產生之成效的延續性或造成的影響，這種評估我們稱為：', '["投入評估", "需求評量", "效果評估", "效率評估"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08235', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有系統地蒐集、分析與工作相關的資訊，並就「工作內容」、「工作脈絡」及「工作條件」予以清楚描述的途徑和過 程稱為：', '["工作分析", "工作規範", "工作說明書", "工作評價"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08236', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '對於一個方案運作的情況進行分析，其實際執行情況為何？其運作是否符合原來的規劃與期待？那些人投入參與了方 案？這項工作稱為：', '["成果評估", "適當性評估", "過程評估", "成本效益評估"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08237', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '一個機構在其所屬社工員在外犯了罪影響其機構及社工專業聲譽後，才發現該社工員在未進入該機構前即有犯罪前科， 但該機構在進用該員時並不知情且未對該員之背景資料做詳細查證，這是下列那一個人力資源管理工作的疏忽所造成：', '["招募", "甄選", "員工培訓", "員工發展"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08238', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '依我國志願服務法第 22 條規定，志工依志願服務運用單位之指示，因故意或過失不法侵害他人權利者，其損害賠償 責任由下列何者負責？', '["縣市政府", "中央政府", "志願服務運用單位", "社會局"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
